div.div: Takagi and Nishikata’s final summer in junior high is about to begin, and it’s already off to a heartwarming start! When the pair find an abandoned kitten, they decide to work together and take care of Hana, their adorable new companion until they can locate its missing mother. What follows is the true beginning of this moving story of young love, complete with the delightful teasing and hilarious antics fans have come to expect from this beloved series and its cast of fan-favorite characters. (Source: Sentai Filmworks, edited)

Ritsu's middle school friend invites the band to perform live on New Year's Eve. The girls get acquainted with other bands, and become a little nervous as the performance approaches. When the time comes, will they be able to rock the house?
(Source: Hidive)

The new serialization features Chi, the daughter of Nishikata and the (former) Takagi-san. As Chi-chan starts junior high school, will she be a teasing master, too?
(Source: Gekkan Sunday, translated)
The adventures of Nishikata Chi in middle school.
